{"tid":1507581,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［解放殖民，香港革命］昨晚，打響了香港革命的第一槍","createTime":"2019-08-26T08:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T18:40:34.000Z","uid":149630,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd76c55ad9536e0dd7f633bf5551f7ac464dd134","tid":1507581,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:14:02.000Z","msg":"昨晚，打響了香港革命的第一槍，這是敵方意外地為我們響起的集結號，令我們無比的惶恐與欣慰。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵方終於用槍聲肯定，我們是認真的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今年是香港的成年禮。</span></span>初生的華英共和國，遇上老大的蘇維埃王朝，注定要大打一場，之後各行各路。你有你鎖國愚昧，我有我開放聰穎。<br />\n所謂反對逃犯引渡條例修訂，只是香港建國戰役的藉口，我們無心保護在港的財閥富豪的家財性命，財閥富豪也無心保護我們的赤裸身軀，彼此漠不關心。我們只是慶幸在這個無事發生的沉悶世界，找到大打一場的浪漫藉口。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們慷慨地將憲政民主的香港，施捨給漠不關心的富豪財閥，一群躲在在高樓廣宅的政治乞丐。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不是時代革命，是香港革命。不要遮遮掩掩，要夠膽講出來。我們從未統治過香港，故此不是光復香港，而是解放香港。</span></span>敵方都為我們開了槍火，不要遮遮掩掩，要夠膽講出來。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">解放殖民，香港革命。</span></span>打完了，香港成人長進，立於強國之林。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國走進來，世界捲入來，做我們建國鬥爭的見證。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n--陳雲"},{"pid":"380b919b19b5645eac804d51ca88ad6935046f9b","tid":1507581,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:14:28.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=05df2d53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"987a15418ccd8cc4303c9dc05274d854bd41efaa","tid":1507581,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:13:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1baa74a0366d00df4442e9f4065966f3b9b57b2d","tid":1507581,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:14:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8504dbdc6cb8e449d534cbac12c2c4ce390147b","tid":1507581,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:14:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"214304f8790d6fa0018035c6fc2cab471c3af43c","tid":1507581,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:06:21.000Z","msg":"藥效退啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c87239346db99696efa68d643211b798f441341","tid":1507581,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:53:58.000Z","msg":"【入嚟填呀！】升級罷工，全民自決。網民發起問卷調查！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508197</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpD40fE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpD40fE.jpg&h=6cea06ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dCmh2k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dCmh2k.jpg&h=274a80cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11bdf3d736bfd4972ce2472e99a65a6ce28dc89c","tid":1507581,"uid":173058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T18:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}